sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as MCP Client (Host + LLM)
    participant S as MCP Server
    Note over C,S: TYPICAL FLOW: Client → Server
    C->>S: tools/call: analyze_data(dataset)
    S->>C: result: {summary: "..."}
    Note over C,S: BIDIRECTIONAL: Server → Client
    S->>C: sampling/createMessage<br/>"Rank these 50 papers by relevance"
    Note right of C: Server borrows<br/>host's LLM
    C->>S: sampling response: {ranked_papers: [...]}
    S->>U: elicitation/request<br/>"Delete production DB? Confirm Y/N"
    Note right of U: Server asks user<br/>for input
    U->>S: "Y"
    S-->>C: notifications/progress<br/>progress: 60/100
    Note right of C: Fire-and-forget<br/>(no response needed)
